lines.text: [the Buds have been called into Musso's office for no apparent reason]
Have we commited any transgression in the last 48 hours?
I had Jerry do a full system sweep.

[Jerry lifts up a stack of prinouts, about three-inch thick, and slams it on the table]
Nothing traceable.
Sirs, I'm going for the salmon!
Madonna? Face of a collie! But she's got...

[dramatic voiceover]
You listen. Listen to a public recital of the secret diary of Parker Lloyd Lewis, Kubiac's ceremony. Hahahahaha! Muahahahahahaha! Muahahahahahahahahaha!
